                <h4>What is the voting age population of Virginia, Illinois?</h4>
                <p>
                    The total voting age population of Virginia, Illinois, meaning US citizens 18 or older, is 1,011.  The voting age population is 47.6% male and 52.4% female.
                </p>
                

                
                
                    <h4>What percentage of Virginia, Illinois residents are senior citizens?</h4>
                    <p>
                        According to the latest census statistics, 19.1% of
                        the residents of Virginia are 65 or older.
                    </p>
                

                
                    

    
    
        
    

    

    
   
    
        <div class="adthrive-content-ad" style="min-height: 120px;">
            
        </div>
    
                    
                    <h4>What are the racial demographics of Virginia, Illinois?</h4>
                    <p>The racial demographics of Virginia are 98.1% White, 0.8% Asian, 0.5% Other, 0.4% Black and 0.2% Two or more races. Additionally, 1.1% of the population identifies as Hispanic.</p>
                

                
                
                    <h4>What percentage of Virginia, Illinois residents are below the poverty line?</h4>
                    <p>
                    In Virginia, 11.6% of
                    residents have an income below the poverty line, and the child poverty rate
                    is 17.8%.
                    On a per-household basis,
                    5.2% of families are below
                    the poverty line in Virginia.
                    </p>
                

                
                
                    <h4>What percentage of Virginia, Illinois residents are in the labor force?</h4>
                    <p>
                    Among those aged 16 and older, 68.3% of
                    Virginia residents are in the labor force.
                    </p>
                

                

    
    
        
    

    

    
   
    
        <div class="adthrive-content-ad" style="min-height: 120px;">
            
        </div>
    

                
                
                <h4>What are the education levels among Virginia, Illinois residents?</h4>
                <p>Among the adult population 25 years old and over,
                    92.2% of
                    Virginia residents have at least a high school degree or
                    equivalent, 17.7%
                    have a bachelor's degree and 4.5%
                    have a graduate or professional degree.
                

                
                
                <h4>What percentage of Virginia, Illinois residents speak a non-English language at home?</h4>
                <p>
                Among Virginia residents aged 5 and older, 0.4% of them speak a non-English language at home.
                Broken down by language:
                0.0% of residents speak Spanish at home,
                0.0% speak an Indo-European language, and
                0.4% speak an Asian language.

                </p>
                

                
    


                
                
                    <h4>What is the unemployment rate in Virginia, Illinois?</h4>
                    <p>
                        The unemployment rate in Virginia is 6.0%, which is calculated among residents aged 16 or older who are in the labor force.
                    </p>

                

                
                
                    <h4>What percentage of Virginia, Illinois residents work for the government?</h4>
                    <p>
                    In Virginia, 20.2% of the
                    residents in the non-military labor force 
                    are employed by the local, state and federal government.
                    </p>
                

                

    
    
        
    

    

    
   
    
        <div class="adthrive-content-ad" style="min-height: 120px;">
            
        </div>
    

                
                
                    <h4>What is the median income in Virginia, Illinois?</h4>
